Function ProcessPurchaseFromWorkshopVendor()
	WorkshopScript thisWorkshop = WorkshopFramework:WSFW_API.GetNearestWorkshop(PlayerRef)
	ObjectReference kCheckMe = kLastPurchaseFromVendorContainer
